<tr><th></th><th>Bitcoin (BTC)</th><th>XRP</th></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Use Case</strong></td><td>Store of value / digital gold</td><td>Cross-border payments &amp; bridge asset</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Supply</strong></td><td>21 million cap (fixed)</td><td>100 billion total (pre-mined, ~50% in escrow)</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Speed &amp; Fees</strong></td><td>~10 minutes / high fees</td><td>3–5 seconds / under $0.01</td></tr>
